version_description:
Thanks for riding with Cabify. If you enjoy using our app, we’d love a nice review (our programmers are very self-critical and in need of constant reassurance!).

In this update we’ve fixed a few bugs and smoothed a couple of rough edges in the hope of making your experience more seamless than ever.

In this update we’ve fixed a few bugs ...oh, and we added support for the iPhone X ;)

Thanks for riding with Cabify. If you enjoy using our app, we’d love a nice review (our programmers are very self-critical and in need of constant reassurance!).

What’s new? Pretty much everything! This is our brand new app and we think you’re going to love it.

Biggest improvements:
- A more attractive, more intuitive design
- We now suggest your usual destinations, so you can just tap and go
- Your route is illustrated on the map
- Reservations are easier to make
- Price options per category visible at a glance
- Battery and data optimization so you don’t run out of juice
- Lots of other improvements.

Thanks for choosing Cabify. We update the app regularly to improve your experience by adding new features, fixing any bugs and making other small tweaks. This release includes:

- You can now order without GPS signal.
- More options available for you to rate your driver.
- Improved push notifications. You can now call your driver or cancel a journey without opening the app.
- Lots of other small improvements and bug fixes.

We've been working to put the whole city in your hands via our app. With this new version you will be able to:
- Verify your identity more easily and quickly when you’re paying by cash. As always, your data will be safe with us.
- Scan your card to add a new payment method more easily.

In addition, we've fixed some bugs and made some small improvements so nothing will stop you when you order your next ride. So, where do you want to go?

We love people who are curious enough to read our What’s new. If you’re here, you’re one of them, so you deserve to get the inside scoop on what’s changed in this version of the app:
- You can now see a detailed price breakdown in your previous journey screens. We’re as clear as day!
- If you choose to pay in cash, we’ll notify you so that you can have your money ready. Of course, you’ll always know the price before you ride.
